  "text": "Joly et al. [CITATION_1] and Dittrich et al. [CITATION_2] increased the platinum dose intensity by adding carboplatin 300 mg/m 2 to cisplatin 100 mg/m 2 (6 CTX); thus reaching a dose-intensity factor for platinum of 1.6, together with an increase in the TCD. However, no survival benefit was found, only increased toxicity.",
